des: "I bartended at a comedy club in Clearwater, Florida. This was one of our specialty drinks. I think you'll enjoy this recipe."
ins: In a blender, combine ice cream, coffee liqueur, banana liqueur and pineapple juice. Blend until smooth. Drizzle chocolate syrup decoratively into a fluted glass.  Pour blended mixture into glasses and garnish with whipped cream and a slice of banana.
